 *
 * protected $message
 * protected $code
 * protected $line
 * protected $file
 * private   $trace
 *
 * 4) Inherited methods from PHP Exception Class:
 *
 * __clone
 * __construct
 * getMessage
 * getCode
 * getFile
 * getLine
 * getTraceSafe
 * getTraceSafeAsString
 * __toString
